wifi-nightmare (2.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging for APT-based install.
  * Pre-compiled ESP firmware bundled in /usr/share/wifi-nightmare/.
  * Runtime data stored in /var/lib/wifi-nightmare/.
  * Configuration overrides in /etc/wifi-nightmare/config.yaml.
  * System dependencies auto-resolved via apt (aircrack-ng, iw, hcxtools, etc.).

